Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.58,0:00:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情  戀愛  推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.48,0:00:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那樣的約定的話就可以堅持到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.48,0:00:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不合季節的推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的心情揭穿案情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看穿真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.48,0:00:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去是小孩  頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴兒  你要振作一點呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.43,0:01:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保持住清醒的意識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  您要冷靜呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.73,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等片刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.03,0:02:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.43,0:02:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既不是撞痕又不是擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了行了  干擾急救可不行呀  小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陷入意識不清的病危狀態了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.23,0:02:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下醫院的搶救工作也會相當艱難呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.93,0:02:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  簡直是絲毫不曾察覺呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.23,0:02:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝高之後  酩酊大醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.33,0:02:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生可是邊睡邊斷案的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.33,0:02:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛  毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非人稱「沉睡的小五郎」的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位毛利先生麼  那位偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「名偵探」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈  這可真是失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經獲得了上級的批准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煩勞您一定要協助我們的調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上級的  這個不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.23,0:03:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.73,0:03:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛與幽靈與地球遺產（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.03,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要被列為地球遺產了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然發生這樣的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我也是這個村子裡長大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望您能爭分奪秒盡快破案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.23,0:03:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.23,0:03:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  既然您這麼懇切地請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.73,0:03:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我小五郎一定全力相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那您就儘管放心好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.23,0:03:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼恕我直言毛利先生  誰是兇手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會真是什麼幽靈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.93,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道些什麼呢  你們這些小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  果然還是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.03,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  就是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  柯南你不是也看見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只不過是什麼東西看起來像她罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道又是洗過的衣服嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過  多虧步美看花了眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.53,0:04:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們才能察覺兇犯逃走的方向呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.23,0:04:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個方向的話  死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.83,0:04:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像無法通行到村外面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.33,0:04:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.23,0:04:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兇犯還沒有逃離這個村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在不像專程從村外闖進來行兇的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連同遊客一併算上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.53,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在兇犯就混在這個鬼澤鄉的眾人之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  你們到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必理會他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.23,0:05:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們所說的那些  連外行都知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.73,0:05:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  你們可不要干擾查案呀  各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.53,0:05:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有件更應該引起我們注意的重要事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.73,0:05:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人在白天觀光時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡繫好了繩索並藏了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.43,0:05:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後  深夜從村外潛入時用到了那根繩索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.13,0:05:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.93,0:05:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人應該是除去毛利先生您所住的永倉家以外的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且就在住宿本村的遊客之內  是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.63,0:05:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是毛利先生  佩服  佩服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.03,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您真是太抬舉我了  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫且不管這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.93,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問題是  犯人在那裡幹了什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.63,0:05:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那閣樓頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,元太  你不要推我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.13,0:06:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點  我們還要再上一層呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是個小偷而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.63,0:06:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是  究竟打算從這裡偷些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來  還是我看錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.33,0:06:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然柯南都那麼說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得好像是看花眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.93,0:06:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.03,0:06:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不是想偷什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.03,0:06:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是絕對是在找什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.23,0:06:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在這的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生被刺傷的現場可真是一目瞭然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.03,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在對面那間屋子也會看得一清二楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南  發現什麼了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.43,0:07:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兒  有什麼情況麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別碰  會中毒發炎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.53,0:07:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是漆樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  永倉先生的手確實是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說永倉先生昨天經過了這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.43,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是昨天那個令人討厭的傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  是他將永倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.73,0:07:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可為什麼村民們會圍著他吵嚷起來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.43,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我倒是知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這兒之前  我在雜誌上讀到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說  本來這個村子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.23,0:07:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞著是否要申請地球遺產的問題而發生了分歧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不希望再增加遊客的反對派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和希望這村子能名聞天下的推進派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.43,0:08:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生應該是那個推進派的代表呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候永倉先生說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是被誰指使的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.03,0:08:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老伴兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是那幫傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「那幫傢伙」原來指的是反對派
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家冷靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給警察來處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.43,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家快些回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼可能  我們要在這裡討個說法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那傢伙逃跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.33,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地球遺產登記委員會派遣來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.03,0:08:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是聽說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有像這樣隱藏自己的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.23,0:08:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公平地判斷是否有申請地球遺產的價值的專職調查員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.23,0:08:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個人的話  這只是表面上的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從各地上繳的自治費用中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為評估人員的活動經費收取可觀的賄賂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧  川治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您在說些什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要裝傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在被害者附近出現過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經掌握了證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來也向永倉先生勒索賄賂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.13,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻不料碰了個釘子  所以你才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.73,0:09:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要亂開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是向他提過錢的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也確實被拒絕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只好就此作罷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備今天就回去  昨晚便早早入睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一步都沒出去過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.03,0:09:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老奸巨滑的你哪能這麼輕易就放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰會相信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.03,0:09:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此我才確實放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.53,0:09:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我多年來的經驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.13,0:09:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣死纏爛打下去也不會有活動經費進腰包的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.63,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.43,0:09:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這  這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生的巡視記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據當天的記錄來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在巡查過第九幢房子時還蓋著「無異常情況」的章印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.13,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生遇襲被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.33,0:10:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在已經蓋上章正走向第九幢房子的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你住宿的石崗先生家旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說又不是我決定要住在那家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.53,0:10:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有誰看到你入睡了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.13,0:10:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時只有我自己  所以沒有任何人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.53,0:10:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不是我幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺傷別人這種愚蠢行為我是不可能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果  川治先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.73,0:10:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被警方作為恐嚇及殺人未遂案件的重要嫌疑人帶走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.13,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而關於其殺人未遂的嫌疑卻完全缺乏證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.43,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於潛入永倉家的情況也完全不詳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起來案件似乎是解決了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.93,0:10:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感謝您了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.33,0:10:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福終於逮捕了川治這小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.53,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒我們是不是要慶祝一下喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.83,0:11:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想說「好呀～」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為有被老婆審訊的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.43,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.43,0:11:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是禍不單行呀  永倉先生家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草草解決了案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.83,0:11:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣反而不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禍不單行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔說的是他們家的兒子永倉榮治吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是很大的意外呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信榮治是無辜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真美找他來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.13,0:11:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起榮治他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的傢伙已經不是我的兒子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.33,0:11:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那件事也算上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.23,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十天前村裡剛舉行過神器轉移的祭祀活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.03,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行了久違三十年的茅屋房頂的修整重葺工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.83,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且把各家各戶的屋子移動到了現在的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.13,0:12:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移動了  那樣巨大的房屋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  那些地基如此的新原來是因為這個緣故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過令人震驚的還遠不止這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.53,0:12:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半個月以前永倉家所在的位置是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對　好像是從這裡搬到了現在的地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.53,0:12:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和原本在那裡的乙澤家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好調換了位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.13,0:12:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說是神器轉移什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.53,0:12:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.93,0:12:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那兒不是整個村裡看起來最好的地點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.23,0:12:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是永倉家作為申請地球遺產的推進派代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,強行搬遷到那兒去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.83,0:12:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有不少人那麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.73,0:12:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真像呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.03,0:12:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.43,0:12:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們是說這間屋子和永倉家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.23,0:13:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是夜裡的話認錯了也不是沒可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.33,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許犯人的動機與是否申請地球遺產全無關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說只是單純地把兩棟房子給弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.73,0:13:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  忽然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.23,0:13:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別  別跑這麼快嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然不出所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.63,0:13:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面也一模一樣嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在永倉先生家裡時應該是在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到什麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.43,0:13:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  太精美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.13,0:13:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  新一呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.33,0:14:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樁寶石搶劫案時被盜的寶石呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來怎麼樣是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像還沒有找到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.23,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方得出的結論是早就被犯罪份子處理掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.93,0:14:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是還沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.23,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪犯逃亡時把那間寶石店的鑒定師綁架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.53,0:14:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,推測說大概是人質沒用之後就被殺害了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好燙呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才　沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.83,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點小事而已  哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.33,0:14:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊麼  柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.03,0:14:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是交給警察比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.43,0:14:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓  你的聲音太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.43,0:14:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真是這真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快  毛利先生  請吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然  真兇是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜恐怕會在那裡出現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.43,0:15:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然還是來了  大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等了你很久呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次絕不會讓你跑掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.43,0:15:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不著  出來散散步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.83,0:15:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果迷了路  和永倉家還真像呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.43,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那些寶石是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.13,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是你一個月前在鄰村的寶石店裡搶來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.93,0:15:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你  你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.73,0:15:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝傻也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.63,0:15:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔　你就是殺害了永倉榮治並且將其偽裝成自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.03,0:15:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寶石搶劫案的主犯  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.73,0:15:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,榮治哥哥好像負債纍纍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是你便以此為由強行要挾他作幫兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說  搶劫寶石和殺害警衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實都是大叔你一個人幹的  對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.33,0:16:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道你在說些什麼呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.73,0:16:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃亡過程中經榮治帶路來到了這鬼澤村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.73,0:16:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把搶來的寶石藏在了已經廢棄的乙澤家的空屋內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過你沒有想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半個月後村裡會調換房屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.03,0:16:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後　你便把罪行都嫁禍給了榮治哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺害了他  並使現場看似自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.73,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而後  又裝成觀光遊客再次來到這個村子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想取走藏起來的贓物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在左手裡拿著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.63,0:16:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不正是那些寶石麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚趁永倉先生外出巡夜不在之機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.83,0:16:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尋找寶石時被我們發現便從窗口逃逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說根本不是從外部潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而本來就在那棟房子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.53,0:17:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這一切卻被在外巡夜的永倉先生撞見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.03,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在永倉先生匆匆忙忙返回自家的路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.03,0:17:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡查記錄上印章的順序之所以可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因就在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.93,0:17:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我  我不過是個糟老頭子而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.93,0:17:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過是來旅行的罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些寶石也不過是偶然發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.43,0:17:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你既不是上了年紀的人也不是遊客 我們很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為早就注意到了你右眼眶周圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.73,0:17:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是放大鏡的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被當作人質劫持又被認為已經慘遭殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去向不明的鑒定師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.43,0:17:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你  板木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.03,0:17:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.13,0:17:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過自從犯人自殺以後 我就一直很害怕躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.63,0:18:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才終於鼓起勇氣來取走寶石的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.33,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是這樣的話你們打算怎麼辦呢  小鬼們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.43,0:18:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說  你承認昨夜曾在永倉家三層尋找寶石了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又能怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之後你從窗口逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刺傷永倉先生的罪行呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀是呀  我喝得太多醉得昏天黑地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說根本不可能進行那樣的犯罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.03,0:18:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你什麼時候在哪裡碰到漆樹了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一起喝酒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.83,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和永倉先生可都還沒有中毒發炎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.03,0:18:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,問問一起就餐的人就能馬上查實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.33,0:18:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過那可正是你們倆曾在同一時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.43,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同一地點的絕佳證據呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永倉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.73,0:18:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全村栽種漆樹的地方可是獨一無二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.53,0:19:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下結案了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.73,0:19:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該死的小鬼們  到底是什麼人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.53,0:19:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶川柯南  偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.83,0:19:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們　少年偵探團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑  還不快給我閃開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.03,0:19:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能被你幾個小鬼抓住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.53,0:19:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 　把榮治還給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.23,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把榮治還給我呀　還給我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  就是現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.83,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.53,0:20:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮  步美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是逼真演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.13,0:20:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奧斯卡影后級的學院水準呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼演技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.93,0:20:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不過安靜地站在這裡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.23,0:20:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站著  那剛才的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是霧  是霧  好好看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.53,0:20:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嵐煙呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.83,0:20:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在飛機上或山頂經常能看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.83,0:20:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是麼  如此說來  那些也都是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  世界上有什麼不能用科學與推理來解釋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.73,0:22:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.63,0:22:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝您昨天的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.03,0:22:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.93,0:22:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托您的福  成功阻止了犯人逃亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.13,0:22:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是您呀  毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.33,0:22:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我松代  真是心服口服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心  心服口服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.23,0:22:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是呀  是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.83,0:22:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真想再見你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕你是幽靈也好  真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.93,0:23:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步美　快點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.03,0:23:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.63,0:23:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了  等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.23,0:23:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調換位置的兩棟茅草屋  各歸原位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.23,0:23:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說後來傷癒的永倉先生感悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.03,0:23:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正是在兒子幼年青梅竹馬的朋友真美的靈魂指引下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.33,0:23:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兒子死因的真相才得以重見天日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.03,0:23:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然作為偵探  堅持理論和推理的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.83,0:23:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不會相信這些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.43,0:23:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後  經過了兩個月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.93,0:23:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鬼澤鄉作為地球遺產正式被登記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.85,0:23:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟犯罪這樣的社會陰暗做鬥爭就是我偵探的本職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.63,0:23:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這大叔做什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.87,0:23:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.69,0:24:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒把天線收回去真是個粗心的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.39,0:24:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是 他想讓人聽到鈴聲並發現手機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.99,0:24:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以故意藏到那裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.64,0:24:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.91,0:24:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三千日圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.77,0:24:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人難道說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.86,0:24:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.27,0:24:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被遺忘的手機(前篇)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.63,0:24:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.56,0:24:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.30,0:24:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.22,0:24:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毛利偵探事務所一樓的咖啡廳叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.85,0:24:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就是買啤酒的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.32,0:00:25.64,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,近日時常夢見你突然離我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.37,0:00:31.21,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,面對惶惑不安的我 你依然無聲無息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.79,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一雙溫暖的手緊握在口袋裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.06,0:00:42.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,糾纏的五指彷彿繽紛的花朵競色爭奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.09,0:00:49.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,即使停駐於憂鬱隱晦的霏霏霪雨 你的身影依然那麼粲然奪目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.23,0:00:55.75,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向著你我約定過的溫柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.90,0:01:01.09,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,而今兩個人依然齊肩攀越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:06.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,遙望你為我彩繪的夢幻季節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:14.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,暫別的時日可以令愛更強烈 直至歲月翻過那一頁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.16,0:01:20.78,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,向著你我約定過的溫柔之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.89,0:01:25.86,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,無謂的逃避只會迷途無措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.39,0:01:31.96,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,縱然漫無標識的路千曲百折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.96,0:01:39.57,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1450)}依循彼此的信任與愛相攜 直至步入那溫柔世界…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.39,0:21:13.67,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的視線相遇之前 心就已經決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.25,0:21:23.91,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,如同正午的月亮一般 雖然看不見 但是知道它在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.79,0:21:36.50,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是孤獨 就算是幸福 一個人的時候又怎能分辨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.94,0:21:47.95,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的相遇 如同在深海中游泳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.68,0:22:01.03,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你沐浴在光芒下呼吸 尋找我們兩人的方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.26,0:22:12.62,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,在圍繞著升起又落下的太陽 旋轉的這個星球上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.90,0:22:19.63,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,看吧緩緩起伏的海面上的月亮
